name: Televan Koreyy
Lore: 'Leader of Tatooine''s Street Performers And Panhandlers'' Guild. Televan can survive on almost nothing, and he keeps tight controls on other Guild members. Information broker.',
Text: 'Beggar and Frozen Assets are canceled. Your thieves, gamblers, and information brokers at related Tatooine sites are power +1. While at Cantina, Mos Espa, or Marketplace, may draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.',
